Class SensorDataGenerator.DataCategory

  • java.lang.Object
    • jimjams.airmonitor.sensordata.SensorDataGenerator.DataCategory
  • Enclosing class:
    SensorDataGenerator

    static class SensorDataGenerator.DataCategory
extends java.lang.Object
    Groups data for a single type of reading. Used to construct SensorData. Instance variable are package-private to allow access from SensorDataGenerator.
